Following my comments, you should not bind your options to a form control. 

Instead, simply create a two-dimensional array like so : 

    groups = [
      { controlName: &#39;first&#39;, options : [{ type: &quot;first&quot;, parameter: &quot;first&quot; }, { type: &quot;first&quot;, parameter: &quot;first&quot; }] },
      { controlName: &#39;second&#39;, options : [{ type: &quot;second&quot;, parameter: &quot;second &quot; }, { type: &quot;second&quot;, parameter: &quot;second&quot; }] },
    ];

    myForm = new FormGroup({
      first: new FormControl(),
      second: new FormControl()
    });

And iterate over it. 

    &lt;form [formGroup]=&quot;myForm&quot;&gt;
      &lt;ng-container *ngFor=&quot;let obj of groups&quot;&gt;
        &lt;mat-form-field&gt;
          &lt;mat-select [formControlName]=&quot;obj.controlName&quot;&gt;
            &lt;mat-option *ngFor=&quot;let option of obj.options | keyvalue&quot; [value]=&quot;option&quot;&gt;
              {{ keyval.parameter }}
            &lt;/mat-option&gt;
          &lt;/mat-select&gt;
        &lt;/mat-form-field&gt;
      &lt;/ng-container&gt;
    &lt;/form&gt;

Keep the options outside of the FormControl, do not set options as the value, you need to handle the options outside of the controls.

HTML:
 
    &lt;form [formGroup]=&quot;myForm&quot;&gt;
      &lt;ng-container *ngFor=&quot;let control of myForm.controls | keyvalue&quot;&gt;
        &lt;mat-form-field&gt;
          &lt;mat-select formControlName=&quot;{{control.key}}&quot;&gt;
            &lt;mat-option *ngFor=&quot;let option of options[control.key]&quot; [value]=&quot;option&quot;&gt;
              {{option.parameter}}
            &lt;/mat-option&gt;
          &lt;/mat-select&gt;
        &lt;/mat-form-field&gt;
      &lt;/ng-container&gt;
    &lt;/form&gt;

TS. Note that we created an options object, with attribute names that has the same name as our controls

    options = {
        first:  [
          { type: &quot;first&quot;, parameter: &quot;first&quot; }, { type: &quot;first&quot;, parameter: &quot;first&quot; }
        ],
        second: [
          { type: &quot;second&quot;, parameter: &quot;second &quot; },
          { type: &quot;second&quot;, parameter: &quot;second&quot; }
        ]
      }
      myForm = new FormGroup({
        first: new FormControl(),
        second: new FormControl()
      });
    
      constructor() {
        this.myForm.controls
      }

